  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Compare neurocognitive testing MMSE (Mini-Mental State Examination) and MoCA (Montreal
      Cognitive Assessment) to candidates aged patients with 1st line treatment of their cancer
      will be received an examination oncogériatric
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
